# Implementation of the ov_mc_mixer service. 

A mixer service is responsible for mixing openvocs client audio conferences. 

# How to start ov_mc_mixer

ov_mc_mixer is build like all executables under the build folder. To start ov_mc_interconnect you may use 

`markus@RB-BA0007:~/openvocs/code$ ./build/bin/ov_mc_mixer`

# How to configure ov_mc_mixer

The mixer need a connection to the resource_manager, which is the local openvocs instance. Host and port must match the listener configuration of the vocs instance. 

A limit for the reconnect interval may be set. 

